#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:1 of
msgid ""
"Classify text content in a series with given labels using a language "
"model."
msgstr "使用语言模型对 Series 中的文本内容进行分类。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:3 of
msgid ""
"A maxframe Series containing text data to be classified. Each element "
"should be a text string."
msgstr "包含待分类文本数据的 maxframe Series。每个元素应为文本字符串。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:6 of
msgid "Language model instance used for text classification."
msgstr "用于文本分类的语言模型实例。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:8 of
msgid "List of labels to classify the text into."
msgstr "用于文本分类的标签列表。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:10 of
msgid ""
"Description of the classification task to help the model understand the "
"context."
msgstr "分类任务的描述，用于帮助模型理解上下文。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:12 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Examples of the classification task, like [{\"text\": \"text...\", "
"\"label\": \"A\", \"reason\": \"reason...\"}], to help LLM better "
"understand your classification rules."
msgstr ""
"分类任务的示例，例如 [{\"text\": \"text...\", \"label\": \"A\", \"reason"
"\": \"reason...\"}]，用于帮助大语言模型更好地理解分类规则。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:15 of
msgid "Index for the output series, by default None, will generate new index."
msgstr "输出 Series 的索引，默认为 None，将生成新索引。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:18 of
msgid ""
"A DataFrame containing the generated classification results and success "
"status. Columns include 'label' (predicted label), 'reason' (reasoning), "
"and 'success' (boolean status). If 'success' is False, the 'label' and "
"'reason' columns will contain error information instead of the expected "
"output."
msgstr ""
"包含生成的分类结果和成功状态的 DataFrame。列包括 'label'（预测标签）、'"
"reason'（推理原因）和 'success'（布尔状态）。如果 'success' 为 False，则 "
"'label' 和 'reason' 列将包含错误信息而非预期输出。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:24 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:49 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.classify:50 of
msgid ""
"**Preview:** This API is in preview state and may be unstable. The "
"interface may change in future releases."
msgstr ""
"**预览版：** 此 API 处于预览状态，可能不稳定。接口在未来版本中可能会"
"发生变化。"

